sequenceDiagram
  participant SPA as React SPA
  participant API as Laravel API
  participant S3 as S3 disk
  participant SFN as Step Functions
  participant SQS as SQS task queue
  participant Worker as Laravel Worker
  participant Textract as Amazon Textract
  participant Bedrock as Amazon Bedrock
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  SPA->>API: POST /api/v1/documents/ocr
  API->>API: Validate PDF and tenant context
  API->>S3: Store original document
  API->>DB: Create original_documents row
  API->>SFN: StartExecution
  API-->>SPA: 202 streamUrl
  SFN->>SQS: Send task textract.ocr with taskToken
  Worker->>SQS: ReceiveMessage
  Worker->>Textract: Start/GetDocumentTextDetection
  Worker->>DB: Save OCR metadata
  Worker->>SFN: SendTaskSuccess
  SFN->>SQS: Send task bedrock.extract with taskToken
  Worker->>Bedrock: Converse for split/extraction
  Worker->>DB: Persist sub_documents and extracted_data
  Worker->>SFN: SendTaskSuccess
  SFN->>SQS: persist.results and dispatch.domain_event
  Worker->>DB: Update workflow completion metadata
  SPA->>API: SSE stream state
  API-->>SPA: document/done/error events
